  "detailed_description": "<h1>Please!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/a0a25b5a96f1eb2894ee90b4cf0461a0.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/a0a25b5a96f1eb2894ee90b4cf0461a0.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/a0a25b5a96f1eb2894ee90b4cf0461a0.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><i>The way you play games is simple!!!<br>Overcome the trap! <br>Complete the mission!<br>But getting there won't be easy!!!</i></strong><br>Dynamic traps and enemies with random spawn!<br>The various traps will drive you to mission failure again and again!<br>But!!! Keep going as you gradually get used to it!<br>This way, everyone will reach their goal <br>and achieve their goal.<br>Why don't you complete the mission for the first time and then try for a speed run or high score?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/61d506fe963f9280b40167655d138ada.webp?t=1763359700\" width=617 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* Avoid obstacles and defeat enemies as you keep running forward. <br>  Defeat enemies with various actions until you reach your destination or achieve your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* Be careful with switches, ropes, and traffic lights, and use them to progress.<br>* Collect coins, energy (by defeating enemies), and other items to make the game easier <br>   and complete the mission faster.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/7d23973e82dcd98e862afc1c386d0dd1.webp?t=1763359700\" width=617 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>*Experience various actions with easy and simple actions.<br>*Randomly generated stages and obstacles create a different experience every time. <br>  No matter how many times you play, you can have a different experience.<br><br>*Enjoy our futuristic level design.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><i>The way you play games is simple!!!<br>Overcome the trap! <br>Complete the mission!<br>But getting there won't be easy!!!</i></strong><br>Dynamic traps and enemies with random spawn!<br>The various traps will drive you to mission failure again and again!<br>But!!! Keep going as you gradually get used to it!<br>This way, everyone will reach their goal <br>and achieve their goal.<br>Why don't you complete the mission for the first time and then try for a speed run or high score?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/61d506fe963f9280b40167655d138ada.webp?t=1763359700\" width=617 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/59e33fb5da889f0fd0eeb6662d3bd1dd.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* Avoid obstacles and defeat enemies as you keep running forward. <br>  Defeat enemies with various actions until you reach your destination or achieve your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6c8058c4d129976850d67cad4cd5ce15.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* Be careful with switches, ropes, and traffic lights, and use them to progress.<br>* Collect coins, energy (by defeating enemies), and other items to make the game easier <br>   and complete the mission faster.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/7d23973e82dcd98e862afc1c386d0dd1.webp?t=1763359700\" width=617 height=51 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.poster.avif?t=1763359700\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.webm?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167600/extras/6264c5e5f52c4bc23631de45a1ecb6f8.mp4?t=1763359700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>*Experience various actions with easy and simple actions.<br>*Randomly generated stages and obstacles create a different experience every time. <br>  No matter how many times you play, you can have a different experience.<br><br>*Enjoy our futuristic level design.",
